    "<h1 style=\"color: #96174e\">Using LLMs to Analyze Sports Game Recaps</h1>\n",
    "\n",
    "<p>In this post, I examined how an LLM can be used to analyze sports game recaps. Sports articles often focus on scores and highlights, but they can miss broader patterns or strategic takeaways.</p>\n",
    "\n",
    "<p>Instead of reading multiple recaps manually, I used the model to identify recurring themes and key moments from a single game summary.</p>\n",
    "\n",
    "<h4 style=\"color:#0707ff\">The Graphic</h4>\n",
    "\n",
    "<p>\n",
    "<img src=\"sports.jpg\" alt=\"LLM analyzing a sports game recap\" width=\"60%\">\n",
    "</p>\n",
    "\n",
    "<h4 style=\"color:#0707ff\">Game Recap Excerpt</h4>\n",
    "\n",
    "<p style=\"background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px;\">\n",
    "The team struggled offensively in the first half but adjusted their strategy after halftime. Strong defensive play and timely scoring allowed them to regain momentum and secure a narrow victory.\n",
    "</p>\n",
    "\n",
    "<h4 style=\"color:#0707ff\">Prompt</h4>\n",
    "\n",
    "<div style=\"background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px;\">\n",
    "<blockquote>\n",
    "Analyze this recap and identify the main turning point and strategic factors that influenced the outcome.\n",
    "</blockquote>\n",
    "</div>\n",
    "\n",
    "<h4 style=\"color:#0707ff\">Response</h4>\n",
    "\n",
    "<div style=\"background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px;\">\n",
    "<blockquote>\n",
    "The main turning point occurred after halftime, when the team adjusted its offensive strategy. Improved defensive performance limited the opponentâ€™s scoring opportunities, while timely offensive plays helped shift momentum and ultimately decide the game.\n",
    "</blockquote>\n",
    "</div>\n",
    "\n",
    "<p>The response clarified the narrative of the game beyond the final score. It highlighted how strategy and momentum played a central role in the outcome.</p>\n",
    "\n",
    "<h1 style=\"color: #96174e\">Reflection</h1>\n",
    "\n",
    "<p>This experiment showed that LLMs can be useful tools for sports analysis, not just summarization. By focusing on patterns and turning points, the model helped extract insight from a short recap.</p>\n",
    "\n",
    "<p>For sports blogging or commentary, this approach can support deeper analysis without requiring advanced statistics.</p>\n",
    "\n",
    "<p>Overall, this use case reinforced that LLMs can assist in interpreting sports narratives and identifying meaningful moments within game coverage.</p>\n"
   ]
